description: The future of mobile cuisine is on its way, thanks to Curbside Urban Cuisine! The wonderful culinary program at Bates Technical College is training their up-and-coming chefs in the real skills needed to own and operate a mobile eatery just like this terrific truck. A food truck full of great flavor and a great cause: Curbside Urban Cuisine is here and it's perfect for you!
name: Curbside Urban Cuisine
